<HEAD>12-Year-Old Girl's Slaying Becomes Rallying Point for Anti-Drug Protesters</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PASCAGUOLA, Miss. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   More than 100 people marched through
